The paper deals with optimization of transmit power and antenna selection in massive MIMO systems, which involves information theory (IT) and networking (NI) concepts. The proposed algorithm is designed to improve system performance, which falls under the category of systems and control (SY). The paper specifically focuses on massive multiuser MIMO, which is a subfield of multimedia (MM) and machine learning (LG) as it involves processing large amounts of data.
